# Recursive Function

A function that calls itself.

### Factorial Using Recursion

```java
public class Main
{
    static int factorial(int n)
    {
        if(n == 0)
            return 1;

        return n * factorial(n - 1);
    }

    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        System.out.println(factorial(5));
    }
}
```

**Output:**

```
120
```

